	@echo "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠉⠉⠉⠀⠈⠉⠉⠉⠉⠉⠉⠉⠀⠉⠉⠁⠀⠉⠉⠉⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀$(RESET)"

%.o: %.cpp
	$(CC) $(CFLAGS) -c $< -o $@

run:
	make re
	./Brain

clean:
	rm -rf $(OBJS) 
	@echo "$(YELLOW)Removing $(NAME) objects files$(RESET)" 

fclean: clean
	rm -rf $(NAME) 
	@echo "$(RED)Removing $(NAME) executable"
	@echo " /###### /##          /#######  /##                 /##"
	@echo "|_  ##_/| ##         | ##__  ##|__/                | ##"
	@echo "  | ## /######       | ##  \ ## /##  /######   /#######"
	@echo "  | ##|_  ##_/       | ##  | ##| ## /##__  ## /##__  ##"
	@echo "  | ##  | ##         | ##  | ##| ##| ########| ##  | ##"
	@echo "  | ##  | ## /##     | ##  | ##| ##| ##_____/| ##  | ##"
	@echo " /######  ####/      | #######/| ##|  #######|  #######"
	@echo "|______/ \___/       |_______/ |__/ \_______/ \_______/"
	@echo "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣀⣤⣤⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
	@echo "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⡶⢿⣿⣿⢿⣿⡿⣦⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀"
